      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Here's a straightforward, honest deal for the budget-savvy buyer! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs reliably and will get you where you need to go, but it does show its age with visible wear inside and out. It's not a showroom piece, but it's a practical, functional ride at a price that reflects its true condition. If you're looking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag, this one deserves a look!",
