      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Ready to hit the road in a car you can count on? This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it's been well maintained and shows only the normal, everyday wear you'd expect from a car that's actually been driven and loved. Everything works as it should, and it's ready to be your dependable daily driver. A great opportunity to get a solid, reliable ride at a fair price!",
