      "description": "Here's a great opportunity for the practical, value-minded buyer! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's got some miles and life experience behind it, with noticeable wear on the interior and exterior, but it remains a functional, drivable car that can get you where you need to go. You're not getting a showroom shine, but you are getting honest transportation at an honest price. If you're looking for a dependable daily driver without the premium price tag, this one deserves a look!",
