    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 and we want to be completely transparent with you about what that entails. The exterior shows significant wear, including visible rust on multiple panels, noticeable dents, and paint that has faded, chipped, and peeled in several areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard trim, and general signs of heavy use over the years. Mechanically, the car does run, but it has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect to budget for repairs before relying on it as a daily driver. There may be fluid leaks, aging belts or hoses, and other components that are past their service life. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in bringing it up to a better standard. We are pricing it accordingly and encourage you to inspect it thoroughly before purchasing.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in fair condition, and we want buyers to have a realistic picture before reaching out. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 you can expect some scratches, minor dents, and paint fading in certain areas, though the overall body structure remains sound. The interior has seen regular use, with noticeable wear on the seats and trim, but everything is functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some maintenance or minor repairs in the near future \u2014 nothing catastrophic, but not trouble-free either. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for a dependable daily driver at a reasonable price, with the understanding that it is not a pristine or like-new vehicle. What you see is what you get, and we're happy to answer any questions or arrange an inspection.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
